What you need to know:  Ngusale said the player will undergo knee operation after six weeks to allow the injury to heal naturally, but will return after four monthsOdhiambo has featured in all Leopards matches since making his Premier League debut in Ingwe’s 1-0 first leg defeat to Sofapaka in November last yearIngwe’s assistant coach Tom Juma said the team missed his versatility and passing skills when they played Tusker FC on Sunday at Kasarani